General.Name: Sprint Bioscience AB
General.Description: Sprint Bioscience AB (publ) develops pharmaceutical products in the areas of cancer and metabolism in Sweden. The company engages in developing VPS34, a drug candidate for the treatment of various types of cancer by using immunotherapies; and PETRA01, a drug candidate for the treatment of cancer. It also focuses on research of products for the treatment of tumor metabolism and nash and diabetes. Sprint Bioscience AB (publ) was founded in 2009 and is based in Huddinge, Sweden.
